\v 20 \x + \xo 10:20 \xt ver. 27; ch. 2:11 \x*In that day \x + \xo 10:20 \xt ch. 4:2 \x*the remnant of Israel and the survivors of the house of Jacob will no more \x + \xo 10:20 \xt [2 Kgs. 16:7; 2 Chr. 28:20, 21] \x*lean on him who struck them, but \x + \xo 10:20 \xt 2 Kgs. 19:14\x*will lean on the \nd Lord\nd*, the Holy One of Israel, in truth.
