\v 22 \x + \xo 10:22 \xt Cited Rom. 9:27, 28 \x*For though your people Israel be as the sand of the sea, \x + \xo 10:22 \xt [ch. 6:13] \x*only a remnant of them will return. \x + \xo 10:22 \xt ch. 28:22\x*Destruction is decreed, overflowing with righteousness.
