\v 6 An \x + \xo 30:6 \xt See ch. 13:1 \x*oracle on \x + \xo 30:6 \xt [ch. 51:9; Ps. 68:30] \x*the beasts of \x + \xo 30:6 \xt [Acts 8:26] \x*the Negeb.
