\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 30:23 \xt [ch. 32:20; Ps. 144:13, 14] \x*And he will give \x + \xo 30:23 \xt [Jer. 5:24] \x*rain for the seed with which you sow the ground, and bread, the produce of the ground, which will be rich and plenteous. \x + \xo 30:23 \xt [Ps. 65:13]\x*In that day your livestock will graze in large pastures,
