\v 29 You shall have a song as in the night when a holy feast is kept, and gladness of heart, \x + \xo 30:29 \xt 1 Sam. 10:5; 1 Kgs. 1:40 \x*as when one sets out to the sound of the flute to go to \x + \xo 30:29 \xt ch. 2:3 \x*the mountain of the \nd Lord\nd*, to \x + \xo 30:29 \xt ch. 26:4; 44:8; Deut. 32:18\x*the Rock of Israel.
