\v 32 And every stroke of the appointed staff that the \nd Lord\nd* lays on them \x + \xo 30:32 \xt Ex. 15:1 \x*will be to the sound of tambourines and lyres. \x + \xo 30:32 \xt ch. 11:15; 19:16; [ch. 2:19]\x*Battling with brandished arm, he will fight with them.
