\v 6 \x + \xo 31:6 \xt [ch. 30:15] \x*Turn to him from whom people\f + \fr 31:6 \ft Hebrew \fq they\f* have \x + \xo 31:6 \xt ch. 1:5\x*deeply revolted, O children of Israel.
